.SH NAME
MontaggioFoto \- Assembling two images over a 10x15 cm paper
.SH SYNOPSIS
\f[B]MontaggioFoto\f[R] [options]* inputfile+
.SH DESCRIPTION
This program gathers two images on a 10x15cm surface
.PD 0
.P
.PD
that you can print on a paper of ypur choice.
